text: Mulern Jean (born September 25, 1992) is a Haitian hurdler. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 100 metres hurdles race but was disqualified in the heats. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Haitian female hurdlers Category:World Athletics Championships athletes for Haiti Category:Olympic athletes of Haiti Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2018 Central American and Caribbean Games
